Subject: Database Schema
Description:
We would like to integrate with PowerBI and would like the Database schema in order to understand what  is available

There is a PDF document with the mappings. Could you please share it.
Solution_Comment__c:
We have only the schema docs for SA 11.0 that I shared with the customer. Reply from the Tech Docs team:

"We do not have any schema documentation beyond 11.0. Creating this documentation will require significant collaboration from the R&D team"

However, the customer was advised to use 3rd party tools like DBeaver to build ER-diagram of the actual database and select the necessary tables.
